{"tid":255392,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟五毛狗有冇人性嫁?","createTime":"2017-05-24T00:51:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T01:04:40.000Z","uid":59526,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0cee04053f0d648de575bf4cc5244bc32a470998","tid":255392,"uid":59526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T00:51:52.000Z","msg":"Manchester 爆一爆 死左22人 仲要有小朋友 <br />\n正常人都會覺得心痛 可惜<br />\n呢班垃撚圾廢柴仲要用呢件事抽水 <br />\n<strong>「戀殖廢青的祖家，就是這樣！」</strong><br />\n我係香港人，同時間係一個係英國生活嘅英國人，我唔在乎邊個係我祖家，我只關心眼前生活嘅社會 <br />\n而且作為人類(As a human being) 我仲有人格,有良知，知道針對平民嘅恐佈襲擎係一件既可惡又賤格嘅懦夫行為 <br />\n而你班豬狗不如竟然為左攻擎英國而抽水散播恐佈言論，有冇良知 有冇人性?<br />\n我睇到好心寒 好唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n祝佢世世代代都做中國人<br />\n利申1: 口德村村民<br />\n利申2：所有戰爭都唔應該影響到平民, 尤其係細路<br />\n<br />\n有冇手足可以幫手Report 個Post同個Page?<br />\n理由係It's harassment or hate speech<br />\n<br />\nPage link： <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%E5%BB%A2%E9%9D%92%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%832-149918838878285/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E5%25BB%25A2%25E9%259D%2592%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%25832-149918838878285%2F&d=10lXKAqoaEf1JWXJ5ZYNmdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=907b2521\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%E5%BB%A2%E9%9D%92%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%832-149918838878285/</a><br />\nPostLink: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/149918838878285/videos/157124124824423/?hc_ref=NEWSFEED\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F149918838878285%2Fvideos%2F157124124824423%2F%3Fhc_ref%3DNEWSFEED&d=10lXKAqoaEf1JWXJ5ZYNmdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=be6cf2bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/149918838878285/videos/157124124824423/?hc_ref=NEWSFEED</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://imgur.com/a/522F6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F